snippet.title: Diana and Roma wear Astronaut HALLOWEEN Costumes with Barbie Space Discovery
snippet.description:
This is a paid advertisement for Barbie. 
Diana needs help from her friend Astronaut #Barbie to learn about space and bring Roma home #YouCanBeAnything! Parents, The Barbie Space Discovery line is available exclusively at Target.
Thanks for watching!
